snippet.title: M.A.V. Gameplay
snippet.description:
This is a gameplay video introduction. If you are trying to see what the game is all about, or how to do certain things in the game, this video will walk you through all of that. Enjoy! 
Don't forget M.A.V. is on Kickstarter : https://www.kickstarter.com/projects/1509489292/617496852?token=1e5f1fc9
Vote for M.A.V. on Steam Greenlight:http://steamcommunity.com/sharedfiles/filedetails/?id=213963346
